Accept pre-vendored repositories with existing marker files, reuse those
repositories even when Bazel classifies their repository rules as local,
and keep Bazel's subprocess environment instead of clearing it before
adding the requested action environment.  Guix uses store paths in the
inherited environment to make tools executable during bootstrap.

